&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Job description:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an Assistant Portfolio Manager to support and report directly to a senior Portfolio Manager. The successful candidate will play a key role in the day-to-day management of a global EM credit portfolio and in supporting active trading strategies.&lt;/p&gt;
