&lt;li&gt;Graduate with a quantitative degree&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to thrive under pressure and multi-task in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional work ethic&lt;/li&gt;
